        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "But the house of Israel says, ‘The way of the Lord is not right.’ Are My ways not right, O house of Israel? Is it not your ways that are not right?"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Yet the Israelites say, ‘The way of the Lord is not just.’ Are my ways unjust, people of Israel? Is it not your ways that are unjust?"
      },
      "nkjv": {
        "version_id": "NKJV",
        "version_name": "New King James Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Yet the house of Israel says, ‘The way of the Lord is not fair.’ O house of Israel, is it not My ways which are fair, and your ways which are not fair?"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "And yet the people of Israel keep saying, ‘The Lord isn’t doing what’s right!’ O people of Israel, it is you who are not doing what’s right, not I."
      }
